@database DzDir.guide
@Node Main "DzDir.guide"

@{b}What is DzDir?@{ub}
	Simply: A really good directory utility. 

@{b}Is it crippled?@{ub}
	NO!
	The shareware version of DzDir is *Fully* usable and configureable. However 
you are encouraged to register if you want to see new versions. 

@{b} Very important information:@{ub}
	All input methods that use files, use their own filelist in a new window. This is 
much like the concept of having temporary sets with databases. It also makes all ac-
tions able to be 100% async, while retaining the familiarity of the two window direc-
tory utility. And you get to see what the children tasks are doing. Perhaps an exam-
ple; when you grep files, the active list's entries are cloned to another window, you 
can then use the original filelist for other action(s). This new window belongs to an-
other MUI application, therefore you could minimise this window before continuing 
with the rest of DzDir. The grep application will continue greping its files while mini-
mised.


